snippet.title: Doom Warrior Teaser
snippet.description:
Pre-release teaser trailer for Doom Warrior, a barbaric PvP dueling game for PC, Mac, Android & iOS. Crush your enemies, watch them beg for death and hear the cries of their women!

http://www.doomwarrior.com
